</LENGTH>
<HEADLINE>
<P>
CAMPAIGN CALENDAR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Upcoming Events 
</P>
<P>
 Sunday: Ventura County Supervisor John K. Flynn kicks off his 1996 reelection 
campaign at a barbecue from 1 to 4 p.m. at Oxnard Community Center, 800 Hobson 
Way, Oxnard.Donation $10. For more information: 486-8976. 
</P>
<P>
 Tuesday: Republican Assembly candidate Brooks Firestone opens new campaign 
headquarters at 809 Presidio Ave. in Santa Barbara from 6 to 8:30 p.m. 
Firestone will face Democratic nominee Mindy Lorenz in the 35th Assembly 
District that includes Ventura, Santa Paula and Ojai. For more information: 
965-1994. 
</P>
<P>
 Fax Campaign Calendar submissions to 658-5576 or mail to 5200 Valentine Road, 
Suite 140, Ventura, CA 93003. Please include contact person and telephone 
number. 
</P>
