 Tiger Woods, 18, was two under par in a 3-and-2 victory over Kevin Riley of 
San Diego. Steve Woods, a senior-to-be at San Jose State, was three under in a 
6-and-4 victory over Chris Berry of Yorba Linda. Mark Johnson, Tim Hart, Steve 
Burdick, Todd Andrews, Kevin Marsh and Ed Cuff also advanced. 
