<HEADLINE>
<P>
SALINAS NAMES NEW ENVOY FOR CHIAPAS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
By Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 President Carlos Salinas de Gortari on Thursday named the head of the 
government Human Rights Commission as his new peace envoy to Mayan rebels in 
the southern state of Chiapas. 
</P>
<P>
 He said Jorge Madrazo Cuellar would be responsible for beginning a new round 
of talks with the rebels of the Zapatista National Liberation Army. Madrazo, a 
