WORLD IN BRIEF; BOSNIA-HERZEGOVINA; MUSLIMS, CROATS PICK A JOINT GOVERNMENT 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Times Staff and Wire Reports 
</P>
