<TEXT>
<P>
 FHP Honored: The FHP Medical Center in Garden Grove recently received an award 
from that city's mayor, Frank Kessler, for its contributions to the 
community.The medical center was named Large Business of the Year. 
</P>
<P>
 The medical center formed a partnership with Ethel M. Evans Elementary School 
in Garden Grove. Center administrator Michael Coleman served as principal for a 
day, twice, and FHP has donated earthquake kits, invited students on tours and 
sponsored a poster contest. 
</P>
