<P>
 Theater conference -- The Times reported incorrectly in Thursday's Calendar 
section that a conference July 9-10 at UCLA sponsored by the Audrey 
Skirball-Kenis Theatre and the S. Mark Taper Foundation will address the need 
for more mid-sized movie theaters. In fact, the conference addresses the need 
for more mid-sized theaters for stage productions. 
